      h1 Carpenter

      = image_tag 'logo.png'

      p Carpenter is a library for building tables with sorting, pagination, and anything else you can imagine. It's built on top of <a href='http://backbonejs.org'>Backbone</a> and <a href='http://marionettejs.com'>Marionette</a>. Think of it like <a href='http://datatables.net'>DataTables</a> for the client-side MVC set.

